snippet.title: Infinity Nikki Version 1.1 [Shooting Star Season] Trailer
snippet.description:
Let shooting stars guide paper cranes on their journey of fulfilling dreams.

Infinity Nikki Version 1.1 [Shooting Star Season] begins on December 30th, 2024! 
 
The official trailer for Version 1.1 [Shooting Star Season] is now live!

Stories of the past still echo in the wind, as new wishes begin a brand-new chapter.
During the season of shooting stars, people come together beneath a starlit sky.
[May paper cranes carry each precious dream, shooting stars shine upon every heartfelt wish, and may every day of the new year shine as brilliantly as the stars in the sky.]
 
——
